{"tid":1680881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple boycotting news conference","createTime":"2019-10-29T05:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T07:35:32.000Z","uid":336302,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"59cae33274ac6495afca091fad1ad6e3fc824f10","tid":1680881,"uid":336302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"這是一個嚴肅的決定，今天起，《蘋果》不會再出席警方就示威活動舉行的例行記者會。<br />\n<br />\n傳媒是社會公器，捍衞公眾知情權是記者的天職，可惜過去多月來，警方記者會不但無法令公眾了解事實，其加諸傳媒身上的限制、詭辯和謊言，把傳媒貶抑為官方傳聲筒，嚴重打擊新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》杯葛警方就示威活動舉行的例行記者會，不代表我們放棄追查真相，要問的問題、要公開的資料、要讓公眾知道的事實，我們會繼續循既有途徑向警方查詢，要警方向巿民問責。<br />\n<br />\n當警員重新展示編號，當政府撤銷限制「起底」的禁制令，真正讓公眾監察警隊時，《蘋果》會考慮重新出席此記者會。<br />\n記者會不是警方的主場，記者會要還給香港人。<br />\n<br />\n【聲明】《蘋果》杯葛警方記者會<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2JuwHTH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JuwHTH&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=f3a51f38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2JuwHTH</a><br />\n==============<br />\n🗳 光復香港 11.24踢走共產黨<br />\n候選人資料 詳見蘋果區選專頁：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2W7lPjM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2W7lPjM&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=11d7a008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2W7lPjM</a><br />\n==============<br />\n📣 召集有心人！半價贊助學生全年睇蘋果<br />\n我要撐學生 / 我是學生：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2PvsUuK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PvsUuK&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=2cd20576\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2PvsUuK</a><br />\n=============<br />\n🍎 新聞有價，用真相對抗不義<br />\n訂閱撐蘋果，每日只需HK$1.68：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2KFbs1f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2KFbs1f&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=8a07e58c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2KFbs1f</a>"},{"pid":"da8fe3fbd056784dd900c5e9fce29b7ef366d84d","tid":1680881,"uid":47605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"ci